    <description>This mechanical hand replacement is made to speed up medical operations. It is somewhat ungainly, which slows down movement slightly.</description>
    <descriptionHyperlinks><RecipeDef>InstallSurgeonHand</RecipeDef></descriptionHyperlinks>
    <thingSetMakerTags><li>RewardStandardLowFreq</li></thingSetMakerTags>
